<p id="notice"><%= notice %></p>

<%= render "shared/breadcrumb_list" %>

<h1>DDI3 Statistics</h1>

<h2>CLS Metrics v.0.2</h2>

<h3><%= Date.today %></h3>

<p>
<em>The Cell Count is the number of ddi3 xml elements generated when the 'xml library' option is used.
<br/>
The Synaptic Density is the ratio of the number of references over the Cell Count.</em>
</p>

<table>

<tr><td><b>Cell Count</b></td><td><%= @instance.totalElt %></td>
</tr>
<tr><td><b>Synaptic Density</b></td><td><%= "%.2f" % @instance.synapticDensity %>%</td>
</tr>

</table>

<h2>Details</h2>
<p>
<em>The sequence count excludes the generated sequences which wrap the loop and ifthenelse children.
</em>
</p>

<p>
<table>
<tr><td>Sequence Constructs</td><td><%= @instance.sequenceCount %></td>
</tr>
<tr><td>Loop Constructs</td><td><%= @instance.loopCount %></td>
</tr>
<tr><td>Ifthenelse Constructs</td><td><%= @instance.ifthenelseCount %></td>
</tr>
<tr><td>Question Constructs</td><td><%= @instance.questionCount %></td>
</tr>
<tr><td>Statement Constructs</td><td><%= @instance.statementCount %></td>
</tr>

<tr class="firstInBlock"><td>Question Items</td><td><%= @instance.qiCount %></td>
</tr>
<tr><td>Question Grids</td><td><%= @instance.qgCount %></td>
</tr>
<tr><td>Code Lists</td><td><%= @instance.csCount %></td>
</tr>
<tr><td>Categories</td><td><%= @instance.categoryCount %></td>
</tr>
<tr><td>Interviewer Instructions</td><td><%= @instance.instructionCount %></td>
</tr>

<tr class="firstInBlock"><td>Managed Representations (Text)</td><td><%= @instance.repTextCount %></td>
</tr>
<tr><td>Managed Representations (Numeric)</td><td><%= @instance.repNumCount %></td>
</tr>
<tr><td>Managed Representations (Datetime)</td><td><%= @instance.repDTCount %></td>
</tr>

</table>
</p>
<p>
